Davido’s first child, Imade Adeleke, will resume house chores from this weekend, Sophia Momodu, has said. The fashion connoisseur made this known in a recent Instagram live with her fans while having a chat with her daughter. On the live video, Sophia told her daughter that she had already pre-informed her father via SMS and decided to personally inform her.   Community leader tasks BBNaija organisers on modest…     Tiwa Savage gets special award in London     Actress Kate Henshaw claims cleaner stabbed   “We have decided that every Saturday from now on I think you should do a chore, every Saturday. “Do you know what the chore will be? You’ll arrange your toys one, and then two you’ll pick all the dirty clothes in your laundry basket in your room and bring it to the pantry and put it by the washing machine, that is your chore every Saturday from now on,” Sophia said. This development is coming a few days after Imade marked her 7th birthday.